{"tid":2042570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓外交部：支持中國訂立港區國安法","createTime":"2020-05-30T01:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T02:19:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5941376b126a303bcecbb1c3bdab03581474360a","tid":2042570,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:49:30.000Z","msg":"北韓外交部表示，支持中國全國人大通過「港區國安法」，指近年來香港的事態嚴重威脅「一國兩制」原則與國家安全，抹黑社會主義國家形象，助長社會混亂，認為是企圖分裂中國的外部勢力及其追隨者陰謀的產物。<br />\n<br />\n北韓外交部指，香港是中國不可分割的一部分，香港問題完全屬於中國內政，任何國家與勢力對此無權說三道四，朝方對於危害香港安定與社會經濟發展的外部干涉行為，表示堅決反對。"},{"pid":"b0987742fee332a309aad397423ae7c2e2abe9f5","tid":2042570,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:49:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1294193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1294193&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=b7e64898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1294193</a>"},{"pid":"fcd0d1fdf101d9506eb4609d78e641e6e06795aa","tid":2042570,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:50:34.000Z","msg":"佢d空殼公司死得"},{"pid":"0744c1289006adeb6d4698d988798a59e481a8af","tid":2042570,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:50:51.000Z","msg":"肥仔真係兩邊討好"},{"pid":"38e4a31ca99a0ef8eb87131496529333b25d937f","tid":2042570,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"成段野似係中國駐北韓官員自己寫返既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fb55f8c70dc5c594d127a7473c0f3562a60e81","tid":2042570,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:51:47.000Z","msg":"搞個北韓關係法囉"},{"pid":"1cdb13b43be520e30007424e926b72473cc1c555","tid":2042570,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re